ampus Marketplace - Complete Run Guide
1. Run Backend Locally

Open terminal:

cd backend
npm install

Start SAM API locally:

sam build
sam local start-api

You should see:

Mounting CreateListingFunction at http://127.0.0.1:3000/listings [POST]
Mounting GetListingsFunction at http://127.0.0.1:3000/listings [GET]
...

Backend URL:

http://127.0.0.1:3000

Test:

http://127.0.0.1:3000/listings
2. Run Frontend Locally

Open a second terminal:

cd frontend
npm install

Set .env:

For local backend:

VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:3000

Run:

npm run dev

Frontend:

http://localhost:5173
